Height Choropleth

choropleth <- data.frame(
  countries = c("France", "Brazil", "China", "Russia", "Canada", "India", "United States",
                "Argentina", "Australia"),
  height = runif(9, 1, 5)
)

choropleth %>% 
  dplyr::arrange(-height) %>% 
  e_color_range(height, color) %>% 
  e_charts(countries) %>% 
  e_geo_3d(height, color)
